Description:
4 BEDROOM BEAUTY!
Enjoy an exceptional level of comfort and quality in this superbly designed double storey Townhouse located in Central Dandenong. This modern, light and bright 4 bedroom home is ready for you to move in and enjoy!
Immaculately presented both inside and outside, this home offers an open plan design with the spacious living area adjoining the kitchen/meals area. The stunning kitchen comes with stainless steel appliances, dishwasher and gas cooking. Downstairs also comprises of a family bathroom and separate laundry. Upstairs you will find four spacious bedrooms, master with ensuite and double vanity. Outside comprises of a small courtyard with garden shed and large double garage.
This spectacular home is within walking distance to Schools, Train Station and the Central Business District of Dandenong!

Description:
listedAS - Spacious, Stylish And Set To Impress!
Impressive from the moment you arrive with its wide frontage and contemporary two storey facade, this grand scale family abode has room for everyone and all of their things too! Enjoy a quiet cul-de-sac position that is also walking distance to Dandenong South Primary School, Andrews Reserve, Dandenong CBD, market, plaza and train station.
The generous interiors boast three dedicated living zones; a formal living room, an open plan kitchen, meals and family area and an enclosed alfresco set up as a theatre room, plus a fourth versatile room which is well suited as a large study, living area, playroom or fifth bedroom. A double garage, powder room and laundry with shower complete the downstairs layout whilst upstairs comprises of four robed bedrooms, two sparkling bathrooms and a spacious retreat with balcony access.
Bonus extras include both ducted heating and evaporative cooling plus a reverse cycle air conditioner, stone benchtops, 900mm wide oven, downlights and feature pendant lighting.
Enjoy dining alfresco under the pergola and let the kids run around in the secure grassed yard. Head off to work or on family adventures via the nearby Dandenong Bypass, Eastlink or South Gippsland Highway.
Grand scale family abode in quiet cul-de-sac location and close to local amenities
Three living spaces, five bedrooms, two bathrooms, powder room and laundry
Ducted heating, evaporative cooling, reverse cycle air conditioner, stone benchtops, 900mm wide oven, downlights and feature pendant lighting
Low maintenance yards with pergola, grassed area, double garage and additional driveway parking
Walking distance to shops, parks, trains, buses and primary school plus nearby Eastlink, Dandenong Bypass and South Gippsland Highway

Description:
The Ultimate Lifestyle Home a true country feel yet with city convenience!
Sale by Set Date: Tuesday 13th August at 5pm (unless sold prior)
Welcome to this majestic beauty with an emphasis on easy living, style and relaxation. Updated throughout for today's modern living, this delightful home will be your haven all year long with an undercover deck that overlooks a secret garden which securely backs onto extensive parkland and walking trails. Your serenity begins here! Complete with three zoned bedrooms, two bathrooms, multiple living zones plus a stunning kitchen this is truly a lifestyle home and it's positioned on approximately 606m2. It is an absolute must see for families that want space, security and a special find.
What's not to love about this charmer! Beyond the lengthy driveway, double lock up garage and front porch, step inside to be greeted by a light filled living room, which boasts a coonara fireplace for blazing winter warmth as well as a split system unit perfect for all weather conditions. Opening up from here is the meals area and superb kitchen which enjoys a plethora of storage space, grand stone benchtops, tiled splashback and modern appliances.
Zoned down the hallway is the first bathroom and carpeted bedrooms, all with ceiling fans and master with BIRs and a split system unit. Tucked at the rear is a multi-purpose room that could easily be an additional bedroom, living space or dining area while having easy access to the laundry & second bathroom.
In this prime position with instant access to Eastlink and the Monash interchange, it is moments away from Dandenong Central, the Plaza, multiple train stations, plenty of primary and secondary schools and so much more. To enjoy this slice of heaven, call us today!

Description:
Sit back and relax
Recently spruced up with fresh paint, floating timber flooring and new blinds this sensational unit offers turnkey access to an attractive lifestyle. The lucky purchaser will be able to relax and enjoy the updated open plan kitchen with its easy clean tile floor, stainless steel appliances and modern cabinetry. Two generously proportioned bedrooms, both with B.I.Rs are located conveniently close to the bathroom thats been recently updated with quality fittings and fixtures. Features include ducted heating, instant gas hot water and satellite TV cabling. Vehicle accommodation is available in the carport which includes direct access to the private, secure backyard. This fabulous home is situated walking distance from shops, Dandenong Hospital and both North Dandenong Primary and Dandenong High Schools. Public transport can be accessed on nearby Heatherton Road and commuters can be on the M1 Freeway in less than five minutes. This one has got it all so, be quick to inspect!

Description:
Dream size block 750m2 - Presentation Perfect!
In-Room Auction Wednesday 24th July from 6.30pm.
Sandown Regency Motor Inn, 477 Princes Hwy, Noble Park
Positioned on a large block measuring 750m2 (approx), this beautifully presented family home with period features throughout is offered for sale for the first time in over 60 years.
The covered front verandah makes a great entrance to the home. The lounge room with french doors and ornate cornices is spacious featuring split system heating and cooling. Central kitchen with adjoining meals area, 3 large bedrooms all with loads of natural light and a central bathroom plus separate toilet. Electronic Veri blinds on northern windows.
For property developers the generous land size lends itself to a versatile multi unit development project. Develop part or the whole of the property depending on your budget. Consideration could also be given to building your dream home and enjoy the extra land size.
Popular location just minutes to central Dandenong, Metro Village parkland and Dandenong Creek trail bike paths. Walk to Dandenong South Primary and easy access to Eastlink.
Excellent opportunity for investors seeking good rental return for many years with a view of developing units or townhouses at some point in the future.
